snippet.title: Sega Saturn - Private Idol Disc - Tokubetsu-Hen Race Queen G (1997)

Private Idol Disc: Tokubetsu-Hen Race Queen G is a Miscellaneous game, developed and published by Sada Soft, which was released in Japan in 1997.
